{"tid":516940,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[Mac] 求救 唔知發生乜事睇唔到一啲網嘅片","createTime":"2018-01-01T23:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T03:31:18.000Z","uid":163362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b0b2a0bdb903ba9503b60d3efe9dee451780d7ba","tid":516940,"uid":163362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T23:21:45.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n上上吓網追劇 之後開個新分頁去下一集嘅時候就自動轉左去呢到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/02/070822_a41279fc36c85d5a3151172df10f6abf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F02%2F070822_a41279fc36c85d5a3151172df10f6abf.jpg&h=80b7bf01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁我之前都有access過啦 都冇乜事<br />\n但今次access 完就再用唔到啲瀏覽器<br />\n<br />\nVM美劇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/02/071032_b04493dd18104b92105f2f212ea1fd0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F02%2F071032_b04493dd18104b92105f2f212ea1fd0f.jpg&h=446887e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n楓林<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/02/071057_08d3fdd5eda600573e04226db05f8023.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F02%2F071057_08d3fdd5eda600573e04226db05f8023.jpg&h=602124dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連用電腦係連登開post都po唔到圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/02/071247_f31acf2f6bbba614ce4b4b82dd9c18c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F02%2F071247_f31acf2f6bbba614ce4b4b82dd9c18c1.jpg&h=bcf80906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖就up左但就冇圖 就算預覽都唔見<br />\n<br />\n想個到底發生乜事 試過allow cookie/ JavaScript 嗰啲 但都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n目前知到Facebook, YouTube, Bookshelf唔需要認證<br />\n但Vm 連登 楓林 呢啲就要 <br />\n<br />\n有冇人知點搞？ 咁耐以黎淨係用黎上過一次pornhub咁大把 除左popcorn time之外只係down過幾隻game（正版）有冇人識解決？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n追追吓game of thrones 冇撚得睇 好頂引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n電腦白痴唔知點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f802a1371e334849b662252c9080e1b8b4e7fac","tid":516940,"uid":1435,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T23:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://elohell.net/public/comments/small/664e88d47e05cbf4f32875316b2d61df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Felohell.net%2Fpublic%2Fcomments%2Fsmall%2F664e88d47e05cbf4f32875316b2d61df.jpg&h=ec2643e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"262b70d5277e5189e95b7329f0e43ccb703af44a","tid":516940,"uid":163362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f802a1371e334849b662252c9080e1b8b4e7fac","tid":516940,"uid":1435,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T23:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://elohell.net/public/comments/small/664e88d47e05cbf4f32875316b2d61df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Felohell.net%2Fpublic%2Fcomments%2Fsmall%2F664e88d47e05cbf4f32875316b2d61df.jpg&h=ec2643e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T23:25:37.000Z","msg":"試左用電腦cap但電腦開po up上黎睇唔到先轉電話po<br />\n廢事send黎send去先用電話影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06c4699e19bfb8f60a980cbc68302e51e56dd4c","tid":516940,"uid":163362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T23:27:36.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf36b0876b145dcb7cea0eb1fc2bb71419b5fcf","tid":516940,"uid":163362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T23:29:22.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" c